STEP 2: UPLOAD YOUR FILES (10 minutes)
──────────────────────────────────────

Option A: Upload via Web Interface (Easiest)
─────────────────────────────────────────────

1. Click "Files" tab in dashboard
2. Navigate to: /home/[username]/
3. Create new directory: "contract-review-app"
4. Click into that directory
5. Upload files one by one:
   • app.py
   • templates/index.html
   • templates/results.html
