🔧 TROUBLESHOOTING COMMON ISSUES
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

ISSUE: "502 Bad Gateway" error
SOLUTION:
   1. Check WSGI file for typos (username must match exactly)
   2. Verify virtualenv path is correct
   3. Check error log for Python errors
   4. Make sure app.py has: if __name__ == "__main__": removed
      (WSGI doesn't need it)

ISSUE: "ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'flask'"
SOLUTION:
   1. Virtualenv not configured correctly
   2. Go to Web tab → Virtualenv section
   3. Verify path: /home/[username]/.virtualenvs/contract-env
   4. Reload the app

ISSUE: "No such file or directory: 'app.py'"
SOLUTION:
   1. Check file path in WSGI file
   2. Should be: /home/[username]/contract-review-app/app.py
   3. Verify files are actually uploaded (check Files tab)

ISSUE: API calls not working / "Connection refused"
SOLUTION:
   1. Free tier has limited outbound connections
   2. Add www.api.anthropic.com to allowed domains:
      • Go to Web tab
      • Scroll to "Whitelist" section (free accounts only)
      • This is a limitation of free tier
   3. Upgrade to Hacker plan ($5/month) for unlimited connections

ISSUE: Uploads not working / "File too large"
SOLUTION:
   1. Free tier has file size limits
   2. Add this to app.py (if not already there):
      app.config['MAX_CONTENT_LENGTH'] = 16 * 1024 * 1024  # 16MB max
   3. Reload app

ISSUE: App is slow
SOLUTION:
   1. Free tier has CPU limits
   2. Optimize by caching results (add later)
   3. Upgrade to paid plan for better performance


