💡 PRO TIPS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

1. ALWAYS TEST LOCALLY FIRST
   Run your app locally before deploying:
   $ python app.py
   Then fix any errors before uploading

2. USE VERSION CONTROL
   Commit changes to GitHub before deploying
   Makes rollbacks easy if something breaks

3. KEEP LOGS CLEAN
   Fix errors immediately when you see them in logs
   Clean logs = healthy app

4. BACKUP REGULARLY
   Download your code weekly (just in case)
   Keep local backups of everything

5. MONITOR API COSTS
   Check Anthropic dashboard weekly
   Set up billing alerts to avoid surprises

6. SET UP STAGING ENVIRONMENT
   Once making money, create a "test" app
   Test changes there before updating live app

